Package: indicator-script-runner
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1, libnotify-bin, python3-gi
Description: Run a terminal command or script from an indicator.
 The user can specify a terminal command or script with parameters and use
 the mouse (or keyboard shortcut where applicable) to execute the
 command/script rather than opening a terminal.